        d: "<span style='color:#ffffff'>Flesh Burn　</span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>%s/8<br /> </span><span style='color:#ffcb4a'>This skill causes the Modo disciple's enemies to feel as if<br /> they have jumped into the fiery pits of Hell itself.<br /> </span><span style='color:#ffffff'>Can only be used in </span><span style='color:#ffff11'>4aDemonic Posture</span><span style='color:#ffffff'>.<br /> </span><span style='color:#11aaff'>Nguyền rủa đa mục tiêu<br /> </span><span style='color:#ffffff;'>Thời gian thi triển: 1 giây.</span>",
